{
  "stem": "5810.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The man had never taken away the paneling, had never hid the hiding place that we were at.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I took one look on the floor, and the tile had the Fleur de lis.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it just came back to me as this is why I was seeing this in my nightmares.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I must say, from that point on I never had the nightmare again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So that was very therapeutic for me and very healing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there oldest son returned home for just a short period of time and then escaped, and I never saw him again.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the searches continued after his escape and his return over there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He picked up some clothes, stayed one night, I believe, and that just went on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Yes, and at that time, by that time, I, I think I had grown up quite a bit.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had seen quite a bit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had seen, oh, [SIGHS] killings on the streets, Jews being dragged out of their homes or being found out, shootings, bombings.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I grew up, and I grew up very, very fast.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I felt that I was the man of the house at that point.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was-- if any-- if we were going to be saved or if anything needed to be done, it was my duty to do that and protect my mother as much as I could.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She, by that time, just was-- she slept, she prayed, she cried, and she sat in that chair for three and a half years never, never to go out, never to go up anywhere, never to see or know anything, just hoping that someday this all will be over.",
      "word_count": 49
    }
  ],
